text: Kentucky Route 519 (KY 519) is a state highway in Kentucky that runs from Kentucky Route 7 southeast of Pomp to U.S. Route 60 and Clearfield Road in southwestern Morehead via Paragon, Lick Fork, and Clearfield. ==Major intersections== ==References== 0519 Category:Transportation in Morgan County, Kentucky Category:Transportation in Rowan County, Kentucky
title: Kentucky Route 519
